Msg 43757 is 09 line(s) on 07/01/90 from WARD CHRISTENSEN
to CLIFF SHARP re: R/SUPER VHS RENTALS?

 Heck, just buy the Colorado Jumbo and be done with it. A VCR backup
is a hack at best. With my Colorado, I can browse thru the backups,
hit a key to see a full directory, tag a file to be restored, etc.
 It is only $279, but you'll probably spend a lot - maybe even an equal
